{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, in Naarden, this was the first time that Ruti and me remember of having religious activities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Ruti believes that my mother conducted Jewish classes at our home in this [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't remember too much about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But Ruti says we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because now, there, there were more Jews, really, in the area than there had been in Heemstede, in Hilversum, in Bussum, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there were various people who were conducting Jewish classes at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I think it was also-- the Nazi occupation tended to bring the Jews closer together with each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Before that, you know, we'd just been Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we'd just been Dutch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But now, with the, the Germans in charge, I think we became more Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We've-- we were beginning to feel that we were different from the others and, and not really the same as we'd always thought before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Ruti just says that we had it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I presume we learned about the festivals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe we started to learn about Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it is interesting that, at the beginning of the war-- the 10th of May 1940, which for us is the beginning of the war-- until the end of it-- when we were liberated in 1945, April-- there were five years.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we started, as far as I know, I don't-- I knew nothing about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when I finished, I knew quite a lot about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I learned it all on, on the way, in, in various ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And never terribly organized, I don't think, but by these sort of classes, maybe, that my mother took in, in our home and again later on in various places in the camps, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were the odd bits here and there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
